  "Title": "webonyx/graphql-php has quadratic validation cost in OverlappingFieldsCanBeMerged via inline fragments",
  "Description": "`OverlappingFieldsCanBeMerged` validation rule has `O(n^2 x m^2)` worst case via flattened inline fragments. The CVE-2023-26144 named-fragment cache does not cover inline fragments. A 364 KB query (200 outer x 100 inner inline fragments) consumes 117 seconds of CPU per request, with no comparison budget and no validation timeout.",
